# The History of CipherWorks

CipherWorks began with a simple goal:

To make secure backup easy for everyone.

The first product, CipherSync, started as an internal backup utility.

As development progressed, the focus shifted from creating backups to helping people protect their businesses.

The philosophy became simple:

"Don't just create backups.

Help customers stay protected."

This document records the milestones, lessons and decisions that shaped CipherWorks.
